para_trans: Government Decision No. -Shaniva-1525 / Q. No.151 / Niwas-2
Government Decision Mr. Chhagan Chandrabhaga Chandrakant Bhujbal, Hon'ble Minister at "Satpura," Malabar Hill, Mumbai
The government has decided to allot government bungalows.
Residence allotted to the Hon'ble Minister for fifteen days after his discharge from office.
It will be mandatory to vacate during the period.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
